<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Tricep-Extension">Tricep Extension</h3>



<p><a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/rope-tricep-extension" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Tricep Extensions</a> are a focused exercise primarily targeting the triceps, the muscles at the back of the upper arms. Typically performed with dumbbells, barbells, or <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/cable-shoulder-workouts" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">cable machines</a>, the exercise involves extending the arms to lift the weight overhead, then lowering it back, effectively strengthening and toning the triceps.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio vimeo-custom"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
